00:30:07.378 --> 00:30:09.460
-Why is he calling your sir?

00:30:09.460 --> 00:30:11.205
-Because he respects me.

00:30:15.300 --> 00:30:17.270
-It is perfectly good.

00:30:20.000 --> 00:30:21.800
-One of these men
actually cared about me.

00:30:21.800 --> 00:30:23.040
-Good move, Josh.

00:30:23.040 --> 00:30:26.571
-But my mother chose this guy.

00:30:26.571 --> 00:30:28.536
-He's a freedom fighter.

00:30:28.536 --> 00:30:32.190
He's going to make an amazing
father to you, Joshie.

00:30:32.190 --> 00:30:34.082
-He was the worst
decision she ever made.

