-You want to be a man, right?

00:30:38.877 --> 00:30:40.280
Like me?

00:30:40.280 --> 00:30:41.200
Higher.

00:30:41.200 --> 00:30:43.040
Don't lie to me.

00:30:43.040 --> 00:30:43.960
-I'm not lying.

00:30:43.960 --> 00:30:45.810
-You're lying to me.

00:30:45.810 --> 00:30:47.970
What you going to do, huh?

00:30:47.970 --> 00:30:49.470
-Jake, take me with you.

00:30:49.470 --> 00:30:51.950
-Sir, are you his father
or legal guardian?

00:30:51.950 --> 00:30:52.639
-No, but I was--

00:30:52.639 --> 00:30:54.430
-Sir, you're going to
have to come with me.

00:30:54.430 --> 00:30:55.918
-Josh!

00:30:55.918 --> 00:30:57.406
-[INAUDIBLE]!

00:30:57.406 --> 00:31:00.878
-Huh, you scared?

00:31:00.878 --> 00:31:04.842
-Guns are supposed
to protect you.

00:31:04.842 --> 00:31:05.342
-Stop!

00:31:10.302 --> 00:31:12.286
-That's all you got?

00:31:16.254 --> 00:31:38.590
